---

<section id="operations" class="community" aria-labelledby="operations-heading">
  <div class="community__inner">
    <p class="community__lede">Operations</p>
    <h2 id="operations-heading" class="community__heading">
      <span class="community__heading-name">Run, observe, recover.</span>
    </h2>

    <div class="community__grid">
      <a class="community__card" href="/runtime-console/cli-and-console/">
        <h3 class="community__card-title">CLI and Console</h3>
        <p class="community__card-body">Know what belongs in runtime commands, Console workflows, Admin API, and SDKs.</p>
        <span class="community__card-cta">Open command map →</span>
      </a>
      <a class="community__card" href="/runtime-console/observability/">
        <h3 class="community__card-title">Diagnostics and traces</h3>
        <p class="community__card-body">Use Console Doctor checks, audit records, and request traces.</p>
        <span class="community__card-cta">Observe requests →</span>
      </a>
      <a class="community__card" href="/operations/troubleshooting/">
        <h3 class="community__card-title">Troubleshooting</h3>
        <p class="community__card-body">Start from a failing SDK or HTTP call and find the failing surface.</p>
        <span class="community__card-cta">Triage a failure →</span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
